  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes with HbA1c of 7.5 - 11%

          -  Willing to make behavior and lifestyle modifications

          -  No previous bariatric surgery (gastric bypass, gastric banding)

          -  Meet additional study criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of substance abuse or chemical dependency with in the last 3 years

          -  Prior GI surgery for morbid obesity or any gastric surgery for conditions other than
             obesity or diabetes

          -  Severe congestive heart failure

          -  Any underlying illness other than diabetes or obesity that affects gastrointestinal
             motility

          -  Currently taking medications for weight loss
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
